@model proj_01_StudentManagementSystem.Models.Student

<h1>Delete Student</h1>

<p>Are you sure you want to delete the following student?</p>

<div>
    <p><strong>Name:</strong> @Model.Name</p>
    <p><strong>Age:</strong> @Model.Age</p>
    <p><strong>Grade:</strong> @Model.Grade</p>
</div>

<form asp-action="DeleteConfirmed" method="post">
    <input type="hidden" id="Id" name="Id" value="@Model.Id" />
    <button type="submit">Delete</button>
    <a asp-action="Index">Cancel</a>
</form>

@* 
Explanation:

Display Student Details:
    Displays the student’s details (Name, Age, Grade) for confirmation before deletion.
Form Submission:
    Submits to the DeleteConfirmed action in the StudentController.
    The Id is passed as a hidden field to identify the student being deleted.
*@